[02:30.83] It's really me
[02:36.38] Really you
[02:37.55] And really me
[02:42.94] It's so hard for us to really be
[02:51.40] Really you
[02:52.79] And really me
[02:57.62] You'll lose me though I'm always really free
[03:19.62] 
[03:12.48] And the mountain moved its eyes
